snippet.title: Strangeloop - C64 - Longplay
snippet.description:
A full playthrough of Strangeloop on the C64.
Not the best run as I backtrack a little in places and theres more efficent routes but I've not played it for years.

I do go and collect the Geiger counter and Sorcery tapes which are useless as far as I can tell. I also take a quick look into A0 which has an odd robot that also seems to be just for decoration. 
If anyone knows otherwise about these objects or this robot please let me know in the comments.

Happy watching!
